## 🎯 Model Routing (3-Tier Auto-Intelligence)

| Complejidad | Modelo | Latencia | Coste | Casos de Uso |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Baja (<30%)** | Haiku 4.5 | ~500ms | $0.0002 | Triage, tests, investigación rápida, subagentes sencillos |
| **Media (30-70%)** | Sonnet 4.6 | 2-3s | $0.003 | Coding, refactor, planificación, debugging |
| **Alta (>70%)** | Opus 4.6 | 4-6s | $0.015 | Arquitectura, seguridad, decisiones críticas, análisis profundo |

**OpenRouter** (fallback):
```bash
export OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-...
export OPENROUTER_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
