## 🧠 Hive-Mind + Swarm Orchestration

### Topología por Tarea

**Hierarchical** (Coding, Refactoring):
```bash
claude-flow swarm init --topology hierarchical --max-agents 8 --consensus raft
```

**Mesh** (Análisis distribuido, Testing):
```bash
claude-flow swarm init --topology mesh --max-agents 12 --consensus byzantine
```

**Adaptive** (Escalado dinámico):
```bash
claude-flow swarm init --topology adaptive --max-agents 15 --self-healing true
```

### Hive-Mind Commands (Consensus Byzantine)

```bash
# Iniciar hive-mind con Raft
claude-flow hive-mind init --consensus raft --heartbeat 300ms

# Spawn agentes con sincronización
claude-flow agent spawn -t coder --hive --role specialist

# Ver estado del consenso
claude-flow hive-mind status --metrics

# Force rebalance (emergencias)
claude-flow hive-mind rebalance --topology mesh
```

