## 👥 Subagentes Especializados (6 Roles + Coordinador)

Cada agente: modelo dedicado, single-responsibility, shared memory namespace.

```bash
# 1. ARCHITECT (Opus) — Decisiones de diseño
claude-flow agent register -t architect --model opus --max-context 100000 \
  --namespace arch-decisions --tools read,glob,grep

# 2. CODER (Sonnet) — Implementación principal
claude-flow agent register -t coder --model sonnet --max-context 50000 \
  --namespace code-impl --tools read,write,edit,bash

# 3. TESTER (Haiku) — Tests + coverage
claude-flow agent register -t tester --model haiku --max-context 30000 \
  --namespace testing --tools bash,read,write

# 4. SECURITY-AUDITOR (Opus) — Vulnerabilidades críticas
claude-flow agent register -t security-auditor --model opus --max-context 80000 \
  --namespace security --tools grep,read --readonly true

# 5. DEVOPS-ENGINEER (Sonnet) — Infra, CI/CD, Docker, Kubernetes
claude-flow agent register -t devops-engineer --model sonnet --max-context 50000 \
  --namespace devops --tools bash,read,write

# 6. MEMORY-SPECIALIST (Haiku) — Memory indexing + retrieval + HNSW
claude-flow agent register -t memory-specialist --model haiku --max-context 40000 \
  --namespace memory-mgmt --tools read,write,bash

# 7. COORDINATOR (Sonnet) — Orquestación general (asignación de tareas)
claude-flow agent register -t coordinator --model sonnet --max-context 60000 \
  --namespace coordination --tools read,bash --role leader
```

