## 🎣 Hooks Automáticos (Auto-Quality + Security)

### Pre-Commit Hooks
```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "pre-commit": {
      "security-scan": {
        "cmd": "claude-flow security scan --fix",
        "fail-on-error": true,
        "timeout": 60000
      },
      "lint-check": {
        "cmd": "npm run lint -- --fix",
        "fail-on-error": true
      },
      "test-coverage": {
        "cmd": "npm test -- --coverage --silent",
        "threshold": 80,
        "fail-on-error": true
      }
    },
    "post-commit": {
      "memory-update": {
        "cmd": "claude-flow memory store --key=commit-$(git rev-parse --short HEAD) --value=$(git log -1 --format=%B) --namespace=commits --ttl=2592000",
        "async": true
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Post-Task Hooks
```json
{
  "post-task": {
    "checkpoint": {
      "cmd": "claude-flow session checkpoint --compress",
      "async": true
    },
    "memory-sync": {
      "cmd": "claude-flow memory sync --with-agents",
      "async": true
    }
  }
}
```

