## 🔐 Security Rules

- [ ] No secrets en source code (grep antes de commit)
- [ ] Validación input en límites del sistema
- [ ] SQL injection prevention: prepared statements siempre
- [ ] XSS prevention: sanitizar HTML output
- [ ] CSRF protection activo
- [ ] Rate limiting en todos endpoints
- [ ] Error messages no revelan info sensible

```bash
# Pre-commit security scan
claude-flow security scan --fix && git add . && git commit -m "security: fix findings"
```

