## 📊 Execution Strategy

### Task Dispatch (Hive-Mind Routing)

```
Tarea llega → COORDINATOR evalúa complejidad
  |
  ├─ Complejidad BAJA (<30%) → TESTER/MEMORY-SPECIALIST (Haiku)
  ├─ Complejidad MEDIA (30-70%) → CODER/DEVOPS (Sonnet)
  └─ Complejidad ALTA (>70%) → ARCHITECT/SECURITY (Opus)

COORDINATOR mantiene estado + checkpoints
Agentes sincronizados vía shared memory namespace
```

### Spawn Multi-Agent Tasks

```bash
# Spawn swarm para feature complexity (simultáneo)
claude-flow agent spawn -t coder --name coder-1 --hive &
claude-flow agent spawn -t tester --name tester-1 --hive &
claude-flow agent spawn -t devops-engineer --name devops-1 --hive &
wait

# Monitoring
claude-flow hive-mind status --metrics --continuous
```

