## 🛠️ Quick Setup Commands

```bash
# 1. Inicializar Ruflo + MCP
claude-flow init --wizard
claude-flow mcp add claude-flow -- npx -y @claude-flow/cli@latest

# 2. Registrar subagentes (arriba en este archivo)
# (Ejecutar cada comando `agent register`)

# 3. Iniciar daemon + doctor
claude-flow daemon start --log-level=debug
claude-flow doctor --fix

# 4. Hive-Mind initialization
claude-flow hive-mind init --consensus raft --heartbeat 300ms

# 5. Memory system setup
claude-flow memory init --backend hnsw --dimension 1536 --ef-construction 200

# 6. Hooks setup
claude-flow hooks config --from-file .claude/hooks.json
```

