## 📚 Memory Commands Quick Reference

```bash
# Store pattern (architecture, decision, pattern)
claude-flow memory store \
  --key "pattern-sysadmin-automation" \
  --value "PowerShell + Python CLI wrapper pattern for Proxmox/AD/Intune tasks" \
  --namespace sysadmin-patterns \
  --ttl 7776000 \  # 90 days
  --tags "automation,infrastructure,devops"

# Search with HNSW
claude-flow memory search \
  --query "authentication mechanisms for microservices" \
  --namespace security-patterns \
  --limit 5 \
  --threshold 0.75

# List all in namespace
claude-flow memory list --namespace sysadmin-patterns --limit 20

# Retrieve exact key
claude-flow memory retrieve \
  --key "pattern-sysadmin-automation" \
  --namespace sysadmin-patterns
```

