## 🎯 Concurrency Rules

- **ALL agent spawning → ONE message**
- **ALL file ops (read/write/edit) → ONE message**
- **ALL bash commands → ONE message OR piped**
- **NO polling after spawn** — trust agents + wait for results
- **Use TaskUpdate for progress tracking** (not logs)

